{"tid":2288312,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"多D支持！黃秋生台灣開店賣叉燒包","createTime":"2020-11-16T11:54:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-16T12:55:39.000Z","uid":32511,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"85a3f47288f93f448d5802b4c412c0bdeb30c881","tid":2288312,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T11:54:03.000Z","msg":"打算移民到台灣的香港藝人黃秋生，打算做一門十分有噱頭的生意，就是開店賣叉燒包。<br />\n1993年，他憑着《八仙飯店之人肉叉燒包》榮獲香港電影金像獎影帝殊榮，他演活兇殘成<br />\n性的殺人重犯，電影至今雖事隔27年，也令人記憶猶新。黃秋生賣叉燒包，肯定有賣點，<br />\n不過做叉燒包絕不容易，於是他特意到香港佐敦人氣中菜廳逸東軒偷師學藝。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/supplement/20201116/LFHBRXOZRNGI7BZ5JAIC2TTYV4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fsupplement%2F20201116%2FLFHBRXOZRNGI7BZ5JAIC2TTYV4%2F&d=Mbax9TUBBsNKvtRo7%2B5fuzbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=57190678\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fsupplement%2F20201116%2FLFHBRXOZRNGI7BZ5JAIC2TTYV4%2F&h=b13c8b62\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/supplement/20201116/LFHBRXOZRNGI7BZ5JAIC2TTYV4/</a>"},{"pid":"c7b056436567687e01c168f2fe083eaa25d7fb34","tid":2288312,"uid":32511,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T11:54:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/BVjJrnp.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FBVjJrnp.gif&h=c6a2ee31&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eb9c042053772c2976bd0a5c595ecb9335cc25c5","tid":2288312,"uid":49336,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T11:55:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1ac9ba1596057351e9860c9e2508f9edb5762707","tid":2288312,"uid":49336,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T11:56:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d920f3352cf3c45a42cde8fcd55081526449b5d1","tid":2288312,"uid":209890,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T11:57:00.000Z","msg":"其實佢搵館長合作有冇得撚<br />\n2個都出名<br />\n2個都反共<br />\n唔會發大達起馬唔會餓先"},{"pid":"2